 game n\u00e0y th\u00ec \u0111\u1eebng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ef1c b\u1ed5 \u00edch trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft ngay sau \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\">SV368<\/a>.<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ban_biet_gi_ve_Blokus\"><\/span><b>B\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Blokus<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Blokus<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y xa l\u1ea1, tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh board game v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn th\u00ec ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eadp tr\u00ecnh v\u00e0 cho ra m\u1eaft d\u1ea1o g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c anh em game th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00e1 m\u1edbi m\u1ebb. B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch t\u00edch h\u1ee3p nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea7u game hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 sinh l\u1eddi th\u00f4ng qua tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i n\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3658\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3658\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3658 size-full\" title=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Blokus\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-blokus-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 b\u1ed9 m\u00f4n Blokus\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-blokus-1-1.jpg?v=1735745476 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-blokus-1-1-300x150.jpg?v=1735745476 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-blokus-1-1-768x384.jpg?v=1735745476 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3658\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 b\u1ed9 m\u00f4n Blokus<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ed9 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd y\u00eau c\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 tham gia c\u1ee7a t\u1eeb hai \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ed1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi, nh\u1edd \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0 ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat gi\u00e2y vui v\u1ebb b\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n. Khi <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Blokus<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p l\u00ean tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn, th\u00ec nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh gh\u00e9p c\u1eb7p ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i trong m\u1ed9t v\u00e1n. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 sinh l\u1eddi s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa \u00fd v\u00e0 y\u00eau th\u00edch \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Chi_tiet_ve_cach_choi_Blokus_can_biet\"><\/span><b>Chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Blokus c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f4ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o b\u1ed9 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y, anh em s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1eafm r\u00f5 c\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i. N\u1ebfu v\u1eabn \u0111ang hoang mang v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2u th\u00ec c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Blokus<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> sau \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cac_chi_tiet_co_ban\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i Blokus, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed3 ch\u01a1i bao g\u1ed3m hai ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u h\u00ecnh d\u1ea1ng kh\u00e1c nhau. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 chi ti\u1ebft c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn s\u1ebd nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ea3ng tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i: Theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Blokus<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> th\u00ec s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh vu\u00f4ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed7i c\u1ea1nh d\u00e0i b\u1eb1ng nhau. Trong t\u1ea5m b\u1ea3ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd chia ra 20 \u00f4 tr\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gh\u00e9p c\u00e1c m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p v\u00e0o.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1c m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p: Nh\u1eefng m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 b\u1ed1n m\u00e0u kh\u00e1c nhau v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh d\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 c\u0169ng v\u1eady, tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u00f4 vu\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf. M\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng l\u00e0 84 m\u1ea3nh chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho b\u1ed1n m\u00e0u, m\u1ed7i m\u00e0u g\u1ed3m 21 m\u1ea3nh. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, theo quy \u01b0\u1edbc th\u00ec s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u1ea3nh t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb 1 h\u00ecnh vu\u00f4ng, 1 m\u1ea3nh hai h\u00ecnh, 2 m\u1ea3nh c\u00f3 ba h\u00ecnh, 5 m\u1ea3nh b\u1ed1n h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 12 m\u1ea3nh c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 5 h\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3660\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3660\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3660 size-full\" title=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Blokus\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-blokus-2.jpg\" alt=\"C\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft trong game\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-blokus-2.jpg?v=1735745556 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-blokus-2-300x150.jpg?v=1735745556 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-blokus-2-768x384.jpg?v=1735745556 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3660\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft trong game<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cach_choi_cu_the\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Blokus<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n t\u00ednh to\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e1c m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 v\u00e0o trong t\u1ea5m b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ea3nh th\u00ec s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3661\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3661\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3661 size-full\" title=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Blokus\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-blokus-3-1.jpg\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-blokus-3-1.jpg?v=1735745587 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-blokus-3-1-300x150.jpg?v=1735745587 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-blokus-3-1-768x384.jpg?v=1735745587 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3661\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, theo <strong>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Blokus<\/strong> m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t m\u00e0u c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u00e1c m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p m\u00e0u \u0111\u00f3. Th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 m\u00e0u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean trong n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 xanh d\u01b0\u01a1ng, v\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ecf, xanh l\u00e1 c\u00e2y. N\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i SV368 th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c chia m\u00e0u s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean. <\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi m\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p n\u00e0o l\u00ean t\u1ea5m b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa th\u00ec tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfm s\u1ed1 m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Quy_dinh_khi_dat_manh_ghep\"><\/span><b>Quy \u0111\u1ecbnh khi \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e1c m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p trong <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Blokus<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n theo c\u00e1c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3. Vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i khi\u1ebfn tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i k\u1ebft th\u00fac qu\u00e1 nhanh ch\u00f3ng. Khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, anh em game th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng quy t\u1eafc sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean b\u1ea3ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i che m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh vu\u00f4ng \u1edf g\u00f3c vu\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1c m\u1ea3nh sau c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m g\u00f3c c\u00e1c m\u1ea3nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f9ng m\u00e0u nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00e1p c\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi nhau.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nh\u1eefng m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p kh\u00e1c m\u00e0u c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1c nhau c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac t\u00f9y \u00fd m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1c m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t xu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea5m b\u1ea3ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111i \u0111\u00fang th\u00ec bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3663\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3663\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3663 size-full\" title=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Blokus\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-blokus-4-1.jpg\" alt=\"Quy \u0111\u1ecbnh khi \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-blokus-4-1.jpg?v=1735747023 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-blokus-4-1-300x150.jpg?v=1735747023 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-blokus-4-1-768x384.jpg?v=1735747023 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3663\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Quy \u0111\u1ecbnh khi \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ket_luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Blokus<\/strong> ban \u0111\u1ea7u nghe c\u00f3 v\u1ebb ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c ra n\u1ebfu d\u00e0nh th\u1eddi gian t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 c\u00e1c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u trong vi\u1ec7c suy ngh\u0129 logic, b\u1ed9 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn. T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 th\u00e2m gia ngay t\u1ea1i SV368 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn c\u00e1c \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"e